{"TopicId":174977,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"RIP Tom Wolfe","CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T15:11:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T15:11:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/15/obituaries/tom-wolfe-pyrotechnic-nonfiction-writer-and-novelist-dies-at-87.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/15/obituaries/tom-wolfe-pyrotechnic-nonfiction-writer-and-novelist-dies-at-87.html\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T21:48:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCrud. Sorry to hear that. That guy had\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EThe Right Stuff\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T21:54:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was the first non-fiction book I read. Inspired me to become a dreamer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"benzman","CreatedById":82512,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T22:20:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Right Stuff got me interested in Edwards Aid Force base and the whole story of the rocket planes and flight test.\u00A0 I owe a lot to Tom Wolfe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-15T22:26:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe also lost \u003Cs\u003ELois Lane\u003C/s\u003E Margot Kidder (someone else with the \u0022right stuff\u0022) yesterday\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.ctvnews.ca/entertainment/canadian-born-superman-actress-margot-kidder-dead-at-69-1.3928740\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.ctvnews.ca/entertainment/canadian-born-superman-actress-margot-kidder-dead-at-69-1.3928740\u003C/a\u003E. That didn\u0027t seem to get noticed here in The Lounge, and I didn\u0027t want to clutter the forum with RIP threads. I wonder if we should start a master\u00A0\u0022RIP thread\u0022 to mourn everyone in one place...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T01:55:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood idea ^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIP Mr. Wolfe\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-16T01:55:55Z\u0022 title=\u002205/16/2018 01:55  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 16, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by LordFerret\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSaint","CreatedById":70033,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-16T15:12:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne of the obits I read today summed him up perfectly: Tom Wolfe wrote a culture-defining book. And then he did it again. And then he did it again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}